extracted_text: The building coverage on any development site shall not exceed 50 percent in the C-2 (19E) zoning district and 75 percent in the C-3 E/W Main Street district. "Building coverage" means the total ground area of a site occupied by any building or structure as measured from the outside of its surrounding external walls or supporting members.
llm_output.rationale: The text explicitly states the maximum building coverage for the C-2 zoning district, which aligns with our definition of max_lot_coverage. It specifies that building coverage includes the total ground area occupied by buildings and structures, measured from the outside of external walls or supporting members.
